  "task_html": "<div class=\"task-block task-blue\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Aufgabe a) &ndash; Wertetabelle</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:0 0 10px 0;\">F&#xFC;lle die Wertetabelle f&#xFC;r <strong>f(x) = 2x &minus; 1</strong> aus.</p>\n  <div class=\"tbl-wrap\">\n    <table>\n      <thead><tr><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">x</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">&minus;3</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">&minus;2</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">&minus;1</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">0</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">1</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">2</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">3</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td class=\"row-label\">f(x)</td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"-7\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"-5\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"-3\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"-1\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"1\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"3\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"5\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"task-block task-blue\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Aufgabe b) &ndash; Wertetabelle</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:0 0 10px 0;\">F&#xFC;lle die Wertetabelle f&#xFC;r <strong>g(x) = &minus;x + 2</strong> aus.</p>\n  <div class=\"tbl-wrap\">\n    <table>\n      <thead><tr><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">x</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">&minus;3</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">&minus;2</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">&minus;1</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">0</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">1</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">2</th><th style=\"background:#2563eb;\">3</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td class=\"row-label\">g(x)</td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"5\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"4\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"3\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"1\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n          <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"-1\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkStation(3)\">&#x2713; &#xDC;berpr&#xFC;fen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetStation(3)\">&#x21BA; Zur&#xFC;cksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-3\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"task-block task-orange\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Aufgabe c) &ndash; Funktionsgraph</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:0;\">Zeichne beide Graphen in ein gemeinsames Koordinatensystem auf Papier. Klicke danach auf &bdquo;Als erledigt markieren&ldquo;.</p>\n</div>",
  "sol_html": "<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>f(x) = 2x &minus; 1:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;\">x: &minus;3, &minus;2, &minus;1, 0, 1, 2, 3</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:10px;\">y: <strong>&minus;7, &minus;5, &minus;3, &minus;1, 1, 3, 5</strong></p>\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>g(x) = &minus;x + 2:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;\">x: &minus;3, &minus;2, &minus;1, 0, 1, 2, 3</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;\">y: <strong>5, 4, 3, 2, 1, 0, &minus;1</strong></p>"
